Package mansionBandit.gameWorld.matter

Class Summary
Bandit A Bandit is any person that has entered the game to play as a thief
Character A character can be a thief or guard(AI) and implements GameMatter
Chest A chest with treasure in it that will benefit the character
Decoration A type of game matter that can not be interacted with
Dimensions The dimensions class used to find out position and size of every item
Door Door is the link between MansionAreas, Looked at as a GameMatter(Just another object)
FurnitureMovable This class is for each piece of furniture that can be moved
FurnitureStatic A couch that can be moved when in certain places
GameMatter All Items come under this title
Grabable All items that can be picked up and put in the inventory
Guard Guard is an enemy of the bandit and can decrease the bandits health bar
Key A key that can be put in inventory, needs to be in inventory in order to unlock certain doors
Knife Kinfe can be used to attack other bandits, or Guards
Movable All the items that can be moved, e.g furniture
Openable This class contains all the objects that are openable
Sellable This class creates the sellable items
Van This class is where the inventory items are stored and values are calculated
 

Enum Summary
Face Declares the six sides of each room
